Package titocc.tokenizer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CodeReader
    Wrapper for Reader interface that reads characters one at a time and keeps track of lines and columns.
    EofToken
    End of file token.
    IdentifierToken
    Word token that is not a keyword.
    IntegerLiteralToken
    Integer literals consist of sequence of digits 0-9, followed by an optional suffix.
    KeywordToken
    Word token that is found in the list of keywords.
    PunctuatorToken
    Operator or other punctuator.
    Token
    Abstract base for all token types.
    Tokenizer
    Main tokenizer class.
    TokenStream
    Stream of tokens that allows marking positions in the stream and returning back to them.
    WordToken
    Common base class for identifiers and keywords.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SyntaxException
    An exception caused by errors in source code.
